# Contributing

Amphib is built on Hiring Agent — and we keep building. Contributions welcome.

## Bugs

Open an issue. Include: description, environment (OS, Python version, commit), steps to reproduce, and logs.

## Features

Check existing requests first, then open a new one with the problem and your proposed solution.

## Code

1. Open an issue to discuss the change.
2. Fork, branch, code.
3. Format with [Black](https://black.readthedocs.io/en/stable/).
4. Keep prompts provider-agnostic.
5. Test with a real resume on Ollama (and Gemini if you have a key).
6. Open a PR.

## Commit style

```
fix: handle en dash date ranges in work parser
feat: add configurable scoring weights
```

Reference the issue number when applicable.

## Conduct

Be respectful. Report issues to the maintainers.

